    "spell_type": "spell",
    "rank": 9,
    "text": "Fleeting notes of a strange and unnatural song fill the air, overtaking the mind. Each target must attempt a Will save when you Cast the Spell, and again the first time you Sustain the spell each round. A creature needs to attempt only one save against the song each round, and you have to keep the same targets when you Sustain the spell.",
